Data...

19:14.834 --> 19:18.166
Is there something else

19:14.834 --> 19:18.166
you require of me, Captain?

19:18.208 --> 19:21.417
Your clarity of thought.

19:21.458 --> 19:25.625
Your objectivity, as always.

19:25.667 --> 19:27.125
Sit down.

19:30.959 --> 19:35.667
Data, it's very possible

19:30.959 --> 19:35.667
that we are about to go to war.

19:35.709 --> 19:40.000
The repercussions of what we do

19:35.709 --> 19:40.000
during the next 24 hours

19:40.041 --> 19:41.375
may be felt for years to come.

19:41.417 --> 19:45.750
I want you to keep a record

19:41.417 --> 19:45.750
of these events

19:45.792 --> 19:48.417
so that history

19:45.792 --> 19:48.417
will have the benefit

19:48.458 --> 19:51.583
of... a dispassionate view.

19:51.625 --> 19:53.041
I will begin immediately, sir.

19:53.083 --> 19:54.750
Is that all?

19:54.792 --> 19:57.083
How is the crew's spirit?

19:57.125 --> 19:58.750
They are

19:57.125 --> 19:58.750
concerned,

19:58.792 --> 20:01.458
of course, Captain,

19:58.792 --> 20:01.458
but confident.

20:01.500 --> 20:03.959
Do you not see that, sir?

20:05.875 --> 20:07.959
Data, unlike King Henry,

20:08.000 --> 20:10.709
it is not easy for me

20:08.000 --> 20:10.709
to disguise myself

20:10.750 --> 20:14.041
and walk among my troops.

20:14.083 --> 20:15.792
That'll be all.

20:28.375 --> 20:31.625
"Now if these men

20:28.375 --> 20:31.625
