20:41.166 --> 20:43.583
Why must we waste time

20:41.166 --> 20:43.583
playing this ridiculous game?

20:43.625 --> 20:45.500
There's more here than

20:43.625 --> 20:45.500
you're telling us.

20:45.542 --> 20:47.125
You're forcing yourself

20:45.542 --> 20:47.125
to hold back.

20:47.166 --> 20:49.417
I have told you

20:47.166 --> 20:49.417
everything relevant

20:49.458 --> 20:50.792
about Nelvana III.

20:50.834 --> 20:52.166
I'm not talking

20:50.834 --> 20:52.166
about the base.

20:52.208 --> 20:54.208
The base is all that matters.

20:54.250 --> 20:55.750
You're lying, Setal.

20:55.792 --> 20:57.709
Go to Nelvana III

20:55.792 --> 20:57.709
and you will see.

20:57.750 --> 21:00.000
We're not going anywhere

20:57.750 --> 21:00.000
until we get to the truth.

21:00.041 --> 21:01.083
You're a spy, aren't you?

21:01.125 --> 21:02.041
No.

21:02.083 --> 21:03.709
Then prove it.

21:03.750 --> 21:05.583
You can begin by telling me

21:03.750 --> 21:05.583
something about the location

21:05.625 --> 21:07.083
and the strength

21:05.625 --> 21:07.083
of the Romulan fleet.

21:07.125 --> 21:08.041
I don't know it.

21:08.083 --> 21:09.291
You're a logistics officer.

21:09.333 --> 21:10.709
For one sector only.

21:10.750 --> 21:12.417
Who was your superior officer?

21:10.750 --> 21:12.417
Admiral Jarok.

21:12.458 --> 21:13.875
The location

21:12.458 --> 21:13.875
of the Romulan bases

21:13.917 --> 21:14.875
along the Neutral Zone?

21:14.917 --> 21:15.917
I don't know.

21:15.959 --> 21:17.500
In your sector?

21:15.959 --> 21:17.500
Irrelevant!

21:17.542 --> 21:19.250
The number of troops

21:17.542 --> 21:19.250
under your admiral's command?

21:19.291 --> 21:22.250
Irrelevant! Irrelevant!

21:25.667 --> 21:27.333
I guess you're right.

21:27.375 --> 21:30.333
It's not worth

21:27.375 --> 21:30.333
playing this game.

21:30.375 --> 21:32.917
Oh, what a fool I've been--

21:32.959 --> 21:38.375
to come looking for courage

21:32.959 --> 21:38.375
in the lair of cowards.

