21:57.959 --> 21:59.417
Ready for launch.

21:59.458 --> 22:01.083
Proceed.

22:06.625 --> 22:08.291
Probe on course.

22:08.333 --> 22:10.834
Sensors are functioning.

22:10.875 --> 22:13.792
Coordinate your analysis

22:10.875 --> 22:13.792
